title: Week 14 preview & Raiders vs Chiefs recap
itunes:title: Week 14 preview & Raiders vs Chiefs recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game previewing each week 14 matchup, and reveal which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Raiders and the Chiefs.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
